<dt>November 29, 2011; U.S. Department of Justice</dt>
<dd><a class="exit" href="http://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/2011/November/11-crm-1545.html">Owner of Houston Health Care Company Pleads Guilty to Defrauding Medicare</a><br />
