<dt>November 28, 2011; U.S. Attorney; Eastern District of Michigan</dt>
<dd><a class="exit" href="http://www.justice.gov/usao/mie/news/2011/2011_11_28_gwashington.html">Southfield Family Practice Doctor, Dr. Gwendolyn Washington, Sentenced To 120 Months For Public Corruption, Illegal Prescription Drug Trafficking And Health Care Fraud</a><br />
